<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd2a82ac-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s5352"><num value="5352">§ 5352.</num><heading> Delivery of Congressional Pictorial Directory</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="iddd2a82ad-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s5352/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content> None of the funds made available in any fiscal year may be used to deliver a printed copy of the Congressional Pictorial Directory to the office of a Member of the House of Representatives (including a Delegate or Resident Commissioner to the Congress).</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="iddd2a82ae-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s5352/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content> This section shall apply with respect to fiscal year 2019 and each succeeding fiscal year.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="iddd2ccb9f-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/244/dB/tI/s117">Pub. L. 115–244, div. B, title I, § 117</ref>, <date date="2018-09-21">Sept. 21, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/2930">132 Stat. 2930</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
